Dear 6Lo WG,

We have IETF 110 online 6lo session scheduled for Thursday, March 11,
2021 13:00-15:00 (UTC).

Following is the draft agenda for the meeting:

https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/110/materials/agenda-110-6lo-00.txt.

We need a couple of minute takers and a jabber scribe. Please let us
know if you would like to volunteer! This will be very much
appreciated.

Presenters,

Please share or upload [1] your slides (in .pdf) by March 8th 2021.


Thanks,
Carles and Shwetha

[1] There is a datatracker feature that allows a logged in user to
upload slides and suggest the chairs that they be added to a session via a
"Propose Slides" button. Feel free to use this feature
viahttps://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/110/session/6lo.

